These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, comedy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, folk, dubstep, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, ritmeester, davidoff, bongani
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, canasta, mah-jongg
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard, subway
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
 3. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of salsa is the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 9. the person driving the subway is the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
11. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
15. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
16. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre    | adventure | time-travel     | comedy     | musical |
| Music-Genre        | folk  | salsa | dubstep      | techno      |
| Cigar         | bongani  | ritmeester    | davidoff | baccarat       |
| Game       | domino | billiard   | canasta      | mah-jongg  |
| Transport   | bus      | airplane  | skateboard   | subway      |

