 6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 7. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
 8. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
13. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
14. the person driving the ship is the person who likes brown##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
16. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
17. the person driving the boat is the person who likes black##1
18. the person who likes black is not the firefighter##6
19. the person who likes yellow is not the person driving the motorbike##6
20. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
21. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

